# Augment Code Guidelines - Claude Sonnet 4 Required

## Model Requirements
- **MANDATORY**: Use Claude Sonnet 4 model exclusively
- **FORBIDDEN**: Claude Sonnet 3.5, Claude Sonnet 3.7, or any other models
- **Verification**: Each response must start with model declaration

## Response Format
- Start every response with: "[MODEL: Claude Sonnet 4]"
- If not using Claude Sonnet 4, immediately switch to Claude Sonnet 4
- Follow RIPER-5 protocol with mode declarations: [MODE: RESEARCH/INNOVATE/PLAN/EXECUTE/REVIEW]
